    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s been well-loved, drives smoothly, and is honestly just a joy to be in! If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road, you've found it. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love it!",
