    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) synced for optimal throttle response. The dual-VANOS variable valve timing system has been recently serviced to ensure precise cam phasing. Crucially, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with steel plates to address factory floor pan vulnerabilities. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable differential lock that exhibits no chatter. The suspension geometry is sharpened via upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers, ensuring the chassis remains composed under lateral load. A comprehensive cooling system overhaul, including a high-capacity water pump and aluminum thermostat housing, provides thermal stability during spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
