    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presenting a sophisticated 2019 Audi A6 that exemplifies a well-cared-for luxury sedan. The exterior is finished in a timeless Mythos Black Metallic that retains a deep, mirror-like shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia as expected with road use, the body lines remain crisp and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium materials. The Valcona leather seats are supple and free of cracks or stains, and the genuine wood inlays provide a warm, elegant touch. Every piece of technology\u2014from the intuitive dual-screen infotainment system to the crisp Virtual Cockpit\u2014is in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and scheduled inspections. The Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable, absorbing road imperfections with ease. This vehicle has been garage-kept, smoke-free, and recently detailed, making it ready for immediate enjoyment by its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
