    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really nice shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a solid, well-cared-for car without the brand-new price tag. It runs great, looks lovely, and has plenty of adventures left in it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
